Have everything attic aficionado like
Shikeke could hope for! Like clammy
atmosphere, for example...

rows.label: qst610305_msg0003
rows.name:
Even have bat creatures living in it!
Is sure sign of high-quality attic,
Shikeke don't mind telling friend.

rows.label: qst610305_msg0004
rows.name:
Is worlds above attic in Jakolo's where
Shikeke stay first night. That attic not
have one lousy bat creature! Outrage!

rows.label: qst610305_msg0006
rows.name:
Oh, right, now Shikeke remember.
Come here for guided tour, not for
find rented accommodation!

rows.label: qst610305_msg0007
rows.name:
Is mean no disrespect to guide Toutour.
Shikeke head back right away.

rows.label: qst610305_msg0008
rows.name: Thanking friends for looking out for!
